    "The subset of variables extracted by municipality (i.e.",
    "meteorological variables, NDVI and elevation) were then spatially upscaled to FU level using population-weighted averages, assigning more weight to these environmental variables in heavily populated areas inside each FU.",
    "This data was extracted from Google Earth Engine 54 and was manipulated using Python (https:// www. python.",
    "org) version 3.7.0.",
    "A graphical visualisation of some variables of the proposed dataset is presented in Fig. 2."
